h3 {White threatens to win material: h3xg4} Bf5 8. c3 {Covers b4} e6 9. Qa4 a6
{Consolidates b5} 10. Be2 Nge7 11. a3 Bg6 12. Rc1 Nf5 13. Bh2 Nd6 14. b4 b5 {
