Bc2 Bxc2 34. Rxc2 {A double rook endgame occured} Rfe8 35. Ree2 (35. e4 Re7 $14
) 35... Re4 (35... Kf5 36. Rc3 $11) 36. Kf2 Rf8+ (36... g4 37. a4 $11) 37. Ke1
