Deflection}) 42. axb5 $18 axb5 43. Ra2 Kd5 (43... Kc7 44. Ra6 h5 45. Rg6 $18)
44. Ra6 (44. Ra5 {makes it even easier for White} Kc6 45. Ra6+ Kd5 $18) 44...
c3 (44... Rh4 45. Rb6 $18) 45. Kd3 c2 46. Ra1 Re6 (46... g4 {is no salvation}
47. Rc1 gxh3 48. gxh3 $18) 47. Rc1 Ra6 (47... Rf6 {cannot change destiny} 48.
Rxc2 Rf1 49. Rc5+ Ke6 50. Rxb5 Rd1+ 51. Ke4 $18) 48. e4+ Ke6 (48... Kd6 {
is not much help} 49. e5+ Kd7 50. Rxc2 $18) 49. Rxc2 Ra3+ 50. Rc3 Ra4 (50...
Ra6 {doesn't do any good} 51. e5 $18) 51. Rb3 (51. Rc6+ $142 {secures victory}
