) 54. Rxh6 Rg3+ 55. Ke2 Rb3 56. e5 Rxb4 57. Kd3 Rb3+ (57... Rc4 58. d5 Rc5 59.
Rh7+ Kc8 60. Ke4 $18) 58. Ke4 Rg3 (58... Rb2 {a fruitless try to alter the
course of the game} 59. Kd5 $18) 59. Kd5 {[%cal Ye5e6] White prepares e6} b4 (
