(2279)-Seiler,A (2228) Neumuenster 2000 1/2-1/2 (37)}) 13. O-O $146 (13. Nc2 a5
14. O-O Be6 15. Nce3 Bg5 16. a3 Ne7 {1/2-1/2 (16) Ortega,L (2460)-Sulava,N 
(2380) Verona 1997}) 13... Bg5 14. Bg4 Ne7 15. Bxc8 Rxc8 16. Nc2 Nxd5 17. Qxd5
Qb6 18. Rad1 Rfd8 19. Qd3 Rc4 20. Nb4 Qa5 21. a3 Qa4 22. Rfe1 a5 23. Nd5 {
Praise the knight!} Qb3 {Black threatens to win material: Qb3xb2} 24. Re2 h5 (
24... g6 25. g3 $14) 25. Rf1 (25. Rde1 Rf8 $16) 25... h4 (25... Rb8 26. Qg3 Bd8
27. Qh3 $16) 26. f4 (26. Qf3 $5 Rc5 27. Qg4 $16) 26... exf4 $11 27. Nxf4 Qa4 $4
(27... Rc5 $142 $11 {and Black can hope to live}) 28. Nd5 $18 Rc6 $4 {shortens
the misery for Black} (28... h3 29. Nb6 Qb3 30. Qd5 $18) 29. Qf3 (29. Rf5 $142
{seems even better} Qc4 30. Qxc4 Rxc4 31. Rxg5 $18) 29... Rd7 $4 {a blunder in
a bad position} (29... Rf8 $142 30. Qf5 Bd8 $18) 30. Qf5 (30. Qg4 $142 {
it becomes clear that White will call all the shots} Qc4 31. Qxg5 Qxe2 32. Nf6+
Kf8 33. Nxd7+ Ke8 34. Qxg7 Qxf1+ 35. Kxf1 Kxd7 36. Qxf7+ Kc8 37. Qf5+ Kd8 38.
Qg5+ Kc7 39. Qe7+ Kc8 40. Qxh4 Rc7 41. Qh8+ Kb7 $18) 30... Rd8 (30... Rcc7 31.
Qxg5 Kf8 32. Rxf7+ Ke8 33. Rf8+ Kxf8 34. Rf2+ Ke8 35. Qh5+ Rf7 36. Qh8+ Kd7 37.
Rxf7+ Ke6 38. Qe8+ Re7 39. Qxe7#) 31. Qxg5 (31. Qxg5 Re8 32. Ref2 Rxc3 33. bxc3
Qd1 34. Rxf7 Qxf1+ 35. Rxf1 Rxe4 36. Qg6 Re2 37. Rf7 Re1+ 38. Kf2 Rf1+ 39. Kxf1
a4 40. Qxg7#) 1-0

