{[%mdl 8192] C55: Two Knights: 4 d3, 4 d4 exd4 5 e5 and Max Lange Attack} 1. e4
e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Nf6 4. d3 Be7 5. Bb3 O-O 6. O-O d6 7. c3 Bg4 8. Nbd2 Re8
$146 (8... Qd7 9. h3 Bh5 10. Nc4 h6 (10... Nd8 11. Ne3 Re8 12. Nf5 Ne6 13. Re1
Bf8 14. Ng3 Bg6 15. d4 exd4 16. cxd4 c5 17. d5 Nc7 18. Bc2 h6 19. Nh4 Bh7 20.
Nhf5 b5 21. b3 Qd8 22. Bb2 g6 23. Ne3 Bg7 24. Rb1 Qe7 25. e5 {Yudasin,L (2505)
-Jigjidsuren,P (2365) Gdynia 1987 1-0 (51)}) 11. Ne3 Nh7 12. g4 Bg6 13. Kg2 Ng5
14. Nh4 Ne6 15. Nhf5 Nf4+ 16. Kg3 Bxf5 17. Nxf5 g6 18. d4 gxf5 19. dxe5 Rfd8
20. Bxf4 dxe5 21. Bxh6 f4+ 22. Kg2 Qxd1 23. Rfxd1 {Yudasin,L (2405)-Zsinka,L 
(2335) Budapest 1982 1-0 (44)}) (8... d5 9. h3 Bh5 10. exd5 Nxd5 11. Nc4 Bf6
12. Re1 b5 13. g4 bxc4 14. dxc4 Nxc3 15. Qxd8 Rfxd8 16. gxh5 e4 17. Nh2 Nd4 18.
bxc3 Nxb3 19. axb3 Bxc3 20. Be3 f5 21. Nf1 Rd3 22. b4 a5 23. bxa5 {Anand,V 
(2505)-Barua,D (2455) New Delhi 1987 1-0 (42)}) (8... h6 9. Nc4 Be6 10. Ne3 d5
11. d4 exd4 12. exd5 Nxd5 13. Nxd4 Nxd4 14. Qxd4 Nxe3 15. Bxe3 Qxd4 16. Bxd4
Bxb3 17. axb3 c5 18. Rfe1 Rfe8 19. Be3 a6 20. Kf1 Kf8 21. Rad1 Red8 22. Ke2 Ke8
23. Kf3 {Volf,Z (2210)-Truta,S (2201) Ljubljana 2009 1/2-1/2 (47)}) 9. Re1 a5
10. Ba4 Rf8 11. Nf1 Rb8 12. h3 Bxf3 13. Qxf3 {White has the pair of bishops} b5
{Black threatens to win material: b5xa4} 14. Bb3 a4 {Black gets more space} 15.
Bd5 Nxd5 16. exd5 Na5 17. g4 (17. Ng3 Bg5 $14) 17... Bg5 18. Ng3 Bxc1 19. Raxc1
b4 (19... g6 20. Qe4 $11) 20. c4 (20. Re4 bxc3 21. bxc3 Nb7 $14) 20... b3 $11
21. a3 Nb7 22. Ne4 Nc5 $2 (22... f6 $142 $11 {is a viable option}) 23. Nxc5 $16
dxc5 24. Rxe5 Qd6 25. Rce1 Qg6 (25... Rbc8 26. R1e3 $16) 26. Qe4 f5 $2 (26...
Qd6 $142 $16) 27. Rxf5 $18 Rxf5 28. Qxf5 Qh6 (28... Qxf5 29. gxf5 Kf7 30. Re6
$18) 29. Qe6+ Qxe6 30. Rxe6 Kf7 31. Ra6 Re8 32. Kf1 g6 (32... Rd8 {does not
save the day} 33. Ra7 Rc8 34. Rxa4 $18) 33. Rxa4 Kf6 (33... Ke7 $18 {praying
for a miracle}) 34. Ra6+ Kg5 35. Re6 Rf8 36. Kg2 Kf4 (36... h5 {does not solve
anything} 37. gxh5 gxh5 38. Rc6 $18) 37. Re4+ Kg5 38. Re7 h5 (38... Kf4 {
hardly improves anything} 39. f3 Kg5 40. Rxh7 $18) 39. gxh5 gxh5 40. Re5+ (40.
Rxc7 $5 {might be the shorter path} Kh4 $18) 40... Kf4 (40... Kg6 {doesn't get
the cat off the tree} 41. h4 $18) 41. Rxh5 Rg8+ 42. Kf1 Ra8 (42... Rg7 {
doesn't change the outcome of the game} 43. a4 $18) 43. Rh7 Rxa3 (43... Rc8 {
cannot change what is in store for ?} 44. h4 $18) 44. Rxc7 Ra2 (44... Ra1+ {
the only chance to get some counterplay} 45. Ke2 Rb1 $18) 45. d6 Rxb2 (45...
Ra1+ 46. Ke2 Rc1 47. d7 Rc2+ 48. Kd1 Rxf2 49. d8=Q Rf1+ 50. Ke2 Re1+ 51. Kxe1
Kf3 52. Rg7 Kf4 53. Qf6+ Ke3 54. Rg3#) 46. d7 Kf3 47. Kg1 Rb1+ 48. Kh2 Rb2 49.
d8=Q Rxf2+ 50. Kg1 Rg2+ (50... Ra2 {doesn't get the bull off the ice} 51. Qf6+
Ke3 52. Qc3 Ra1+ 53. Kg2 Ra2+ 54. Kg3 Rg2+ 55. Kxg2 Kf4 56. Rxc5 Ke3 57. Re5+
Kf4 58. Qd4#) 51. Kh1 (51. Kf1 $5 b2 52. Qf6+ Ke3 53. Qe5+ Kxd3 54. Rd7+ Kc2
55. Qe4+ Kb3 56. Qd3+ Ka4 57. Ra7+ Kb4 58. Rb7+ Ka4 59. Qb3+ Ka5 60. Ra7#)
51... b2 52. Rb7 Re2 (52... Rc2 {is not the saving move} 53. Rf7+ Ke2 54. Qe7+
Kd2 55. Rf2+ Kc3 56. Qe1+ Kb3 57. Qd1 b1=Q 58. Qxb1+ Kc3 59. Rxc2+ Kxd3 60. Qb2
Ke4 61. Re2+ Kf4 62. Qf6+ Kg3 63. Re3#) 53. Qf6+ Kg3 (53... Ke3 {does not help
much} 54. Re7+ Kxd3 55. Qf3+ Kxc4 56. Qxe2+ Kb4 57. Re4+ c4 58. Qxc4+ Ka5 59.
Re5+ Kb6 60. Rb5+ Ka6 61. Qa4#) 54. Rg7+ (54. Rg7+ Kxh3 55. Qh6#) 1-0

