{[%mdl 8192] C06: French Tarrasch: 3...Nf6 4 e5 Nfd7 5 Bd3 main lines} 1. e4 e6
2. d4 d5 3. Nd2 Nf6 4. e5 Nfd7 5. Bd3 c5 6. c3 Nc6 7. Ne2 Qb6 8. Nf3 Be7 9. O-O
f6 10. exf6 (10. Nf4 Nd8 11. Re1 f5 12. Bxf5 exf5 13. Nxd5 Qc6 14. Nxe7 Kxe7
15. d5 Qa6 16. d6+ Kf7 17. Qd5+ Ke8 18. e6 Nf6 19. d7+ Ke7 20. Qxc5+ {1-0 (20)
Verduga Zavala,D (2250)-Toth,P (2320) Nice 1974}) 10... Nxf6 11. dxc5 $146 (11.
Ng3 O-O 12. a3 cxd4 13. cxd4 Bd7 14. b4 Bd6 15. b5 Na5 16. Ne5 Rac8 17. Bg5 Be8
18. Qa4 Bxe5 19. dxe5 Nd7 20. Qb4 Nxe5 21. Bxh7+ Kxh7 22. Qxf8 Qxb5 23. Qd6
Nac4 24. Qxe6 Bd7 25. Qe7 Re8 {Nasunov,M (2200)-Grigoryan,A (2256) Elista 2014
1-0 (37)}) 11... Bxc5 12. b4 Be7 (12... Bd6 13. Be3 Qc7 14. Ned4 $14) 13. a4 e5
14. a5 {White threatens to win material: a5xb6} (14. b5 e4 15. Be3 Qc7 $14)
14... Qc7 $11 15. Bb5 O-O 16. h3 {Secures g4} Be6 17. Ng3 (17. a6 Bd6 $11)
17... a6 {Black threatens to win material: a6xb5} 18. Be2 (18. Bxc6 bxc6 19.
Be3 Bd6 $11) 18... Rad8 (18... e4 19. Ng5 Bd7 20. c4 $15) 19. Bd2 (19. Qb3 h6
$11) 19... Bf7 (19... Ne4 $142 $5 $17) 20. Ng5 $11 Bd6 21. Nf5 Qd7 (21... Ne7
22. Nxd6 Qxd6 23. Re1 $11) 22. Nxd6 $14 Qxd6 23. Nxf7 {White forks: d6+d8} Rxf7
{White has the pair of bishops} 24. Qb3 Ne4 {Black threatens to win material:
Ne4xd2} 25. Be1 Rdf8 (25... Ng5 26. Rd1 $11) 26. Bh5 (26. Rd1 $5 {should be
considered} Nf6 27. f3 $14) 26... Rf6 27. Rd1 {White threatens to win material:
Rd1xd5} Ne7 (27... Ng3 28. Rxd5 Qe6 29. Bg4 $11) 28. f3 Ng3 $4 (28... Qc6 $142
{was a good chance to save the game} 29. Bg4 R6f7 $11) 29. Bxg3 $18 g6 30. Bg4
h5 31. Bh4 hxg4 (31... R6f7 32. Bxe7 Qxe7 33. Qxd5 hxg4 34. fxg4 $18) 32. Bxf6
Rxf6 (32... Qxf6 {cannot undo what has already been done} 33. fxg4 Qe6 34.
Rxf8+ Kxf8 35. Rf1+ Kg7 36. Qd1 $18) 33. fxg4 Kg7 (33... Rxf1+ {hardly
improves anything} 34. Rxf1 Nc6 35. c4 $18) 34. Rxf6 Qxf6 35. Rf1 (35. c4 {
keeps an even firmer grip} Nc6 36. cxd5 Nd8 $18) 35... Qg5 (35... Qc6 {doesn't
change anything anymore} 36. Qc2 Qe8 37. Qf2 $18) 36. c4 d4 (36... Nc6 37. cxd5
Nd4 38. Qc4 $18) 37. b5 e4 (37... Ng8 {doesn't get the cat off the tree} 38.
bxa6 bxa6 39. c5 Qe3+ 40. Qxe3 dxe3 41. c6 $18) 38. c5 Qxc5 (38... Nd5 39. c6
bxc6 40. bxa6 Qe3+ 41. Qxe3 dxe3 $18) 39. Qf7+ Kh6 (39... Kh8 {does not
improve anything} 40. Qf8+ Ng8 41. Qxc5 Nh6 42. Rf8+ Ng8 43. Qe7 e3 44. Qf7 e2
45. Rxg8#) 40. Qf8+ Kg5 41. h4+ (41. Qf4+ Kh4 42. g5+ Kh5 43. Qg4#) 41... Kxh4
(41... Kxg4 {cannot change what is in store for ?} 42. Qf4+ Kh5 43. g4+ Kxh4
44. Qh6+ Qh5 45. gxh5 g5 46. Kh2 axb5 47. Qe6 Kxh5 48. Qf7+ Kh4 49. Qh7+ Kg4
50. Qh3#) 42. Qh6+ Kxg4 (42... Qh5 {doesn't do any good} 43. gxh5 g5 44. Qd6 g4
45. Qxe7+ Kg3 46. Qd6+ Kh4 47. Qf6+ Kxh5 48. Rf5#) 43. Rf4+ Kg3 44. Qh4# 1-0

