{B01: Scandinavian Defence} 1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5 3. Nc3 Qa5 4. d3 c6 (4... g6
5. Bd2 Bh6 6. Bxh6 Nxh6 7. h3 Nc6 8. Nge2 Nf5 9. a3 Be6 10. b4 Qe5 11. Ne4
O-O-O 12. g3 Ncd4 13. Bg2 Nxc2+ {0-1 (13) Naumov,A (2212)-Reprintsev,A (2428)
