10. f4 O-O-O 11. Bg2 e6 12. Bxc6 bxc6 13. h5 Bh7 14. Qf3 Nd5 15. Nxd5 Qxd5 16.
Bc3 f6 17. Qxd5 cxd5 18. Ne2 Bd6 19. O-O-O {Pueyo Burrel,D (2167)-Ibanez
Tarradellas,E (2267) Barcelona 2015 1/2-1/2}) 5. Be2 Nf6 6. Nf3 Bg4 $146 (6...
Bf5 7. Nd4 Bg6 8. Bf3 e5 9. Nb3 Qc7 10. Be3 Nbd7 11. Nd2 Bb4 12. Nde4 Nxe4 13.
Bxe4 Bxe4 14. dxe4 Bxc3+ 15. bxc3 Nf6 16. f3 O-O 17. O-O Rfd8 18. Qe2 Qa5 19.
Qc4 Nd7 20. Qb4 Qc7 21. Rfd1 {Nelsen,A (2251)-Bock,J (2251) Kleve 2001 0-1 (57)
}) 7. h3 {White threatens to win material: h3xg4} Bh5 8. O-O e6 {Prevents
intrusion on d5} 9. a3 {Covers b4} Nbd7 10. Be3 Be7 11. Re1 O-O 12. Nd4 Bg6 13.
Bf3 Qc7 14. Ne4 Rad8 15. Nc3 a6 {Controls b5} 16. Qd2 Bd6 17. Nde2 (17. g3 $5
$11 {looks like a viable alternative}) 17... Ne5 $17 0-1

