$146 {Black has a cramped position} (4. c3 Nge7 5. Bd3 Bd7 6. h4 g6 7. h5 Bg7
8. h6 Bf8 9. Bg5 b6 10. Bf6 Bxh6 11. Rxh6 Nf5 12. Bxf5 Nxe5 13. Bxd8 {1-0 (13)
