5. Nf3 Ng6 6. c3 Be7 7. Bd3 b6 8. O-O a5 9. Qa4 O-O 10. f5 Nh8 11. Be3 Qe8 12.
f6 gxf6 13. Qc2 fxe5 14. Bxh7+ Kg7 15. dxe5 f5 16. exf6+ Bxf6 17. Bd3 Qh5 18.
Na3 Bd7 19. Nb5 {Rumpf,T (2252)-Bruemmer,F (2237) Germany 2004 0-1 (44)}) 5.
Nf3 Qe7 6. c3 Bd7 7. Bd3 O-O-O 8. O-O Qf7 9. b4 Kb8 10. a4 Nge7 11. Nbd2 a5 12.
bxa5 Nxa5 13. Ba3 Nec6 14. Bxf8 Rhxf8 15. Qc2 Qh5 16. h3 Qh6 17. Nh2 f5 18. Rf2
g5 {Papp,G (2571)-Petenyi,T (2457) Slovakia 2013 1-0 (58)}) 4... Bb4+ (4...
Nge7 5. Bd3 $11) 5. c3 $14 {White threatens to win material: c3xb4} Ba5 6. Bd3
Nge7 7. Ne2 Bb6 8. O-O O-O 9. Nd2 Bd7 10. a4 a6 {Consolidates b5} 11. b4 Nb8 (
11... Nf5 $5 $14) 12. Nf3 c6 (12... Nbc6 13. a5 Ba7 14. Qc2 $16) 13. Ng3 Qc7 $4
{the pressure is too much, Black crumbles} (13... Nf5 $142 $16) 14. Bxh7+ $1
$18 {touch・} Kxh7 (14... Kh8 15. Ng5 g6 16. Qg4 Rg8 17. Bxg8 Kxg8 18. Qh3 Kf8
19. Qh8+ Ng8 20. Nh7+ Ke7 21. Bg5+ f6 22. Bxf6+ Kf7 23. Qg7+ Ke8 24. Qxg8#) 15.
Ng5+ Kg8 16. Qh5 Re8 17. Qxf7+ Kh8 18. Nh5 Rg8 (18... Qxe5 {cannot change
destiny} 19. dxe5 Rg8 20. Nf6 Be8 21. Qxe8 gxf6 22. Qh5+ Kg7 23. Nxe6#) 19.
Qxe7 (19. Nf6 Be8 20. Qxe8 gxf6 21. Qh5+ Kg7 22. Nxe6#) 19... Be8 $18 20. Qxc7
Bxc7 21. Nf4 Bd7 (21... Nd7 $18 {is still a small chance}) 22. Ng6# 1-0

