{A48: 1 d4 Nf6 2 Nf3 g6: Torre, London and Colle Systems} 1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 g6
3. Bf4 Bg7 4. e3 d6 5. Nbd2 O-O 6. c3 c5 (6... Nbd7 7. Bc4 Qe8 8. O-O e5 9. Bg5
a6 10. a4 b6 11. Ne1 Bb7 12. f4 Nd5 13. Nc2 exd4 14. exd4 Ne3 15. Nxe3 Qxe3+
16. Rf2 h6 17. Bh4 Nf6 18. Bxf6 Bxf6 19. Qg4 d5 20. Bb3 c5 21. Nf3 {Nogueiras
Santiago,J (2570)-Jimenez Fraga,P (2402) Ciego de Avila 2010 1/2-1/2 (33)}) (
6... Nh5 7. Bg5 h6 8. Bh4 f5 9. Be2 g5 10. Bg3 Qe8 11. Ng1 Nf6 12. Qb3+ Kh8 13.
f4 g4 14. h3 Nh5 15. Nf1 e5 16. fxe5 Nxg3 17. Nxg3 dxe5 18. d5 f4 19. Ne4 Qg6
20. Nf2 gxh3 21. gxh3 {Draganic,S (2161)-Cop,T (2301) Grubisno Polje 2014 0-1 
(33)}) 7. Bd3 Nc6 8. Qe2 $146 (8. O-O cxd4 9. exd4 e5 10. Bg5 h6 11. Bxf6 Qxf6
12. d5 Nb8 13. c4 Na6 14. a3 Nc5 15. Ne4 Nxe4 16. Bxe4 Qd8 17. Nd2 Qb6 18. b4
Qd4 19. Qe2 f5 20. Bc2 b5 21. Rfd1 Qb6 22. cxb5 e4 {Brkic,A (2208)-Mamedov,R 
(2230) Oropesa del Mar 2000 1/2-1/2}) 8... a6 {Consolidates b5} 9. h3 {
Prevents intrusion on g4} b5 10. O-O c4 {Black threatens to win material: c4xd3
} 11. Bc2 d5 (11... Re8 12. a4 Bb7 13. axb5 axb5 14. Rfd1 $11) 12. e4 $14 dxe4
13. Nxe4 {White has an active position} Nd5 {Black threatens to win material:
Nd5xf4} 14. Bg3 Nb6 (14... Bf5 15. Rfe1 $14) 15. a3 (15. Nc5 Nd5 $16) 15... Bf5
$14 16. Rad1 Bxe4 17. Bxe4 Nd5 {The knight is not easily driven from d5} 18.
Rfe1 e6 {Covers d5+f5} 19. Ne5 {White threatens to win material: Ne5xc6} Qc8 (
19... Rc8 20. a4 $14) 20. Bf3 (20. Bxd5 exd5 21. Qf3 Nxe5 22. dxe5 Re8 $16)
20... Ra7 21. Qd2 Nxe5 22. Bxe5 Rd7 23. Bxg7 Kxg7 {Black king safety dropped}
24. Qe2 Kg8 {Black king safety improved} 25. Qe5 Qc7 26. Qxc7 Rxc7 27. Bxd5
exd5 {A double rook endgame occured.} 28. Re5 {White threatens to win material:
Re5xd5} Rd8 29. Rde1 Kf8 30. f4 Rc6 31. Kf2 Rdd6 32. Kf3 a5 33. Re8+ Kg7 34.
Rb8 Rb6 35. Rxb6 {White forks: b5+d6} Rxb6 36. Re5 {White threatens to win
material: Re5xd5} Rd6 37. Re1 h5 (37... Rb6 38. f5 $11) 38. g4 $14 Kf6 (38...
b4 39. axb4 axb4 40. cxb4 hxg4+ 41. hxg4 $11) 39. g5+ Kg7 40. h4 (40. Re5 $142
