7. O-O Bg4 8. h3 Bh5 9. Re1 Nh7 10. g4 Bg6 11. Nbd2 h5 12. Nf1 hxg4 13. hxg4
Nf6 14. N3h2 Qd7 15. Be3 Rh4 16. Bg5 Rh7 17. Bxf6 gxf6 18. Ng3 Bxf2+ 19. Kxf2
Rxh2+ 20. Kf3 Rh4 {Bores,R (2163)-Vltavsky,V (2177) Czechia 2012 0-1}) (6. Nbd2
d6 7. Bb3 (7. Nf1 O-O 8. Ng3 Ne7 9. O-O Bb6 10. a4 c6 11. b4 a5 12. h3 Ng6 13.
b5 d5 14. Bb3 Re8 15. Qc2 Nf4 16. d4 Nxe4 17. Nxe4 Bf5 18. Re1 Bxe4 19. Rxe4
dxe4 20. Nxe5 Rxe5 21. dxe5 Nd3 {Presalovic,M (2167)-Krajnak,J (2192) Slovakia
2008 1-0 (40)}) 7... O-O 8. h3 d5 (8... Be6 9. Bc2 d5 10. Qe2 d4 11. c4 a6 12.
Ba4 b5 13. cxb5 axb5 14. Bxb5 Nb4 15. Qd1 Bxa2 16. O-O c6 17. Bc4 Qe7 18. Bxa2
Nxa2 19. Nc4 Nxc1 20. Qxc1 Nd7 21. Qc2 Bb4 22. Ra4 Qc5 23. Rxa8 {Maiorov,O 
(2404)-Kuderin,D (2153) Anapa 2009 1/2-1/2 (48)}) 9. Qe2 Re8 10. Nf1 Be6 11.
Bc2 b5 {1/2-1/2 (11) Komliakov,V (2510)-Skatchkov,P (2415) Moscow 1998}) 6...
O-O 7. O-O d6 8. Bb3 a6 9. Be3 (9. Re1 b5 $11) 9... Bxe3 10. fxe3 {White has
new doubled pawns: e3+e4} Ne7 11. Nh4 Be6 12. Bc2 (12. Bxe6 fxe6 13. Nd2 Rb8
$11) 12... c6 13. d4 Qc7 14. Nd2 b5 15. Rxf6 gxf6 {Black wins the exchange} 16.
Qh5 Kh7 17. Rf1 Ng8 18. d5 {White threatens to win material: d5xe6} Bc8 19.
Ndf3 Ra7 (19... Qb6 $5 $11) 20. Nh2 $14 Qd8 (20... c5 21. Nf5 Bxf5 22. Qxf5+
Kh8 23. Ng4 $14) 21. Ng4 (21. dxc6 Rc7 $16) 21... Bxg4 22. Qxg4 (22. hxg4 b4
23. Nf5 bxc3 $18) 22... c5 $4 (22... Ne7 $142 $11 {had to be tried to avoid
defeat}) 23. Nf5 (23. Nf5 Re8 24. Qg7#) 1-0

