{[%mdl 8192] A48: 1 d4 Nf6 2 Nf3 g6: Torre, London and Colle Systems} 1. d4 Nf6
2. Nf3 g6 3. Nc3 Bg7 4. Bf4 d6 5. e3 (5. Qd2 h6 6. h3 g5 7. Bg3 Bf5 8. e3 Ne4
9. Nxe4 Bxe4 10. Bd3 Bxd3 11. cxd3 Nd7 12. O-O e6 13. Rac1 O-O 14. a4 Nf6 15.
Qb4 b6 16. Rc6 a5 17. Qc4 Ne8 18. e4 Qe7 19. Re1 Rd8 {Prie,E (2529)-Vaisser,A 
(2515) Belfort 2010 1-0 (46)}) 5... O-O 6. Be2 Bg4 $146 (6... Nbd7 7. O-O Re8
8. h3 b6 9. Bc4 Bb7 10. Bh2 e5 11. dxe5 dxe5 12. Qe2 Ne4 13. Nxe4 Bxe4 14.
Bxf7+ Kxf7 15. Qc4+ Kf8 16. Qxe4 Nc5 17. Qc4 Qe7 18. Rad1 Bf6 19. Nd2 a5 20.
Ne4 Nxe4 21. Qxe4 {Sakhatova,E (2330)-Kim,O (2250) Yerevan 1996 1-0 (66)}) 7.
h3 {White threatens to win material: h3xg4} Bd7 8. Qd2 Nc6 9. O-O-O Nh5 10.
Rdg1 (10. Bg5 $5 $14 {has some apparent merit}) 10... Nxf4 $11 11. exf4 e5 12.
fxe5 dxe5 13. dxe5 Nxe5 14. Nxe5 Bxe5 15. Bc4 (15. f4 Bg7 $15) 15... g5 (15...
Bc6 16. Qxd8 Raxd8 17. f3 $17) 16. g3 {Controls f4} (16. Qd5 $142 Bxc3 17. bxc3
$11) 16... Bxc3 $4 {throwing away the advantage} (16... Bc6 17. Nd5 b5 $17) 17.
Qxc3 $16 Be6 18. f4 Bd5 (18... Bxc4 19. Qxc4 c6 20. Qc5 $16) 19. Bxd5 (19. Rd1
c6 $18) 19... Qxd5 $16 20. b3 f6 (20... Rad8 21. Rd1 Qf5 22. Kb2 $16) 21. Rd1
Qf7 22. Rhf1 h6 (22... Qg7 23. Rfe1 $16) 23. g4 (23. fxg5 hxg5 24. h4 Qg7 $18)
23... Qg7 24. Kb1 Rad8 25. Rxd8 Rxd8 26. fxg5 hxg5 (26... fxg5 $142 27. Qc4+
Kh8 $16) 27. Qxf6 $4 {simply marches past the door to victory.} (27. Rxf6 Rd1+
28. Kb2 Rd5 $16) 27... Qxf6 (27... Rd1+ $142 $1 {and Black wins} 28. Rxd1 Qxf6
$19) 28. Rxf6 $16 Rd1+ 29. Kb2 Kg7 30. Rf3 c5 $2 (30... Rd2 $142 $5 $16) 31.
Rf5 $18 Rh1 $2 (31... Kg6 32. Rxc5 Rd7 $18) 32. Rxg5+ Kf6 (32... Kh6 {does not
solve anything} 33. Rxc5 Rxh3 34. Rc7 $18) 33. Rxc5 Rxh3 34. Rc7 Rg3 (34... a5
{is no salvation} 35. Rxb7 Rh8 36. Ra7 $18) 35. Rxb7 a5 36. Rb6+ (36. Ra7 $142
{seems even better} Ke6 37. Rxa5 Rg2 $18) 36... Kg5 (36... Ke7 {cannot change
destiny} 37. Ra6 $18) 37. Rb5+ Kxg4 (37... Kf4 38. a4 Rxg4 39. Rxa5 Rg6 $18)
38. Rxa5 Kf4 39. Rc5 Ke4 40. a4 Kd4 41. Rc8 Rg7 (41... Rg6 {is not much help}
42. a5 Kd5 43. b4 $18) 42. Rc4+ Kd5 (42... Ke3 {is not the saving move} 43. b4
Ra7 44. a5 $18) 43. Ka3 Rb7 (43... Ra7 $18 {hoping against hope}) 44. a5 Ra7
45. Ka4 Ra6 (45... Ke5 {what else?} 46. b4 Ra8 $18) 46. Kb5 Ra8 47. a6 Kd6 48.
Ka5 Kd7 (48... Kd5 49. Kb6 Rb8+ 50. Kc7 Rg8 51. a7 Ke5 52. Kb7 Kd5 53. a8=Q
Rxa8 54. Kxa8 Ke5 55. Ka7 Kd5 56. Rc8 Ke5 57. b4 Ke6 58. b5 Kf7 59. b6 Kf6 60.
b7 Ke6 61. b8=Q Kd5 62. Qb7+ Ke6 63. Rf8 Kd6 64. Qe4 Kd7 65. Kb6 Kd6 66. Rd8#)
49. b4 Rh8 50. b5 Rc8 51. Rxc8 Kxc8 52. Kb6 (52. a7 $5 Kd7 53. b6 Ke8 54. a8=Q+
Kf7 55. b7 Kf6 56. b8=Q Kf5 57. Qf3+ Kg6 58. Qg8+ Kh6 59. Qh3#) 52... Kb8 53.
c4 Ka8 (53... Kc8 {doesn't change anything anymore} 54. a7 Kd7 55. c5 Ke6 56.
a8=Q Ke7 57. Qe4+ Kf7 58. Qf5+ Kg7 59. c6 Kh8 60. Qd7 Kg8 61. c7 Kh8 62. c8=R#)
