{[%mdl 8256] C78: Ruy Lopez: Archangelsk and Mler Defences} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3
Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 Nf6 5. O-O Bc5 6. c3 O-O 7. d4 exd4 (7... Bb6 8. Bg5 h6 9.
