{[%mdl 8192] D03: 1 d4 d5 2 Nf3 Nf6 3 Bg5, including Torre Attack with early ..
.d5} 1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5 cxd5 4. Nf3 Nf6 5. c3 e6 (5... Nc6 6. Bf4 g6 7.
Be2 Bg7 8. O-O O-O 9. Nbd2 Nh5 10. Be3 Qd6 11. Re1 f5 12. Nb3 f4 13. Bd2 Kh8
14. Bd3 Bg4 15. Be2 Rae8 16. Ng5 Bxe2 17. Rxe2 e5 18. dxe5 Nxe5 19. Nd4 h6 20.
Ngf3 {Turov,M (2490)-Burmakin,V (2530) Moscow 1994 1/2-1/2 (42)}) 6. Bg5 $146 (
6. Bf4 Bd6 7. Bg3 O-O 8. Bd3 Nc6 9. Nbd2 Qc7 10. O-O Rb8 11. Re1 b5 12. b4 a5
13. a3 Bxg3 14. hxg3 a4 15. Qe2 Ba6 16. Rac1 Ne7 17. Ne5 Nd7 18. Ndf3 Nxe5 19.
dxe5 Rfc8 20. Nd4 Qb6 {Matjushin,G (2349)-Shkuran,D (2231) Evpatoria 2001 1-0 
(56)}) 6... Be7 7. Nbd2 O-O 8. Bd3 h6 {Black threatens to win material: h6xg5}
9. Bh4 b6 10. Qe2 a5 11. a4 Ba6 12. O-O Bxd3 13. Qxd3 Nbd7 14. Nb1 Ne4 15. Bxe7
{White forks: f8+d8} Qxe7 16. Nfd2 Ndf6 17. f3 {Covers g4} Nd6 18. Re1 Nd7 19.
Na3 Rfc8 20. Nb5 {A classical outpost} Nc4 21. Nxc4 Rxc4 22. b3 {White
threatens to win material: b3xc4} Rc6 23. Re2 Qf6 24. Rc1 Qf4 {Black threatens
to win material: Qf4xc1} 25. Qd2 Qh4 26. Qe1 Qg5 27. Rec2 e5 (27... Rd8 28. g3
$11) 28. Re2 $14 f6 29. Rcc2 Re8 30. c4 {White threatens to win material: c4xd5
} (30. Qd1 e4 31. c4 f5 $14) 30... Qg6 $14 31. Rc1 Qf7 32. Rc3 (32. Qd2 Rf8 $14
) 32... Kf8 (32... dxc4 33. bxc4 Qf8 34. d5 $11) 33. cxd5 Qxd5 34. Rxc6 Qxc6
35. Re3 Rd8 36. Qc3 (36. Rc3 Qd5 37. Rc4 exd4 38. Rxd4 Qc5 $11) 36... Qxc3 $11
37. Rxc3 exd4 38. Nxd4 Nc5 39. Rxc5 bxc5 40. Ne6+ {White forks: c5+d8} Ke7 41.
Nxd8 Kxd8 {A pawn endgame occured} 42. Kf2 Kc7 43. Ke3 Kc6 $2 (43... Kd6 44.
Ke4 Ke6 45. f4 f5+ 46. Kd3 $11) 44. Ke4 $14 f5+ 45. Kxf5 (45. Ke5 f4 46. g3
fxg3 47. hxg3 $16) 45... c4 $4 (45... Kd5 $142 $11 {was much better}) 46. bxc4
