-Estrada Nieto,J (2249) Kecskemet 2013 0-1}) (10... Ng4 11. Rf1 Be6 12. Bxe6
fxe6 13. Bf4 $15) 11. Rf1 (11. Be3 Bxe3 12. fxe3 Be6 13. Bxe6 fxe6 $11) 11...
Bg4 $15 12. Bf4 (12. Bd5 Nc5 $15) 12... O-O (12... O-O-O 13. Nbd2 Nxd2 14. Nxd2
$17) 13. Nfd2 (13. Nc3 Nxc3 14. bxc3 h6 $15) 13... Nxd2 $17 14. Nxd2 Nd4 (14...
