Bxc4 17. Rxc4 Ne2+ 18. Kf1 Nxf4 19. Rxf4 Rad8 {Black threatens to win material:
Rd8xd2} 20. Nc4 Rd4 (20... Rfe8 21. g3 $11) 21. Rxd4 Bxd4 22. Rd1 {White
threatens to win material: Rd1xd4} Bb6 (22... c5 $142 $5 $11 {is worthy of
consideration}) 23. Rd7 $16 Rc8 24. f4 g6 25. Ke2 Bg1 26. Ne3 Kf8 (26... Bxe3
27. Kxe3 b5 28. Ke4 $16) 27. Ng4 c5 $4 {Black crumbles in face of a dire
situation} (27... Bc5 $142 $16) 28. Nf6 (28. Nh6 $5 {and White can already
relax} Bh2 29. Kf3 g5 30. Rxf7+ Ke8 31. fxg5 Bxe5 32. Rxh7 Bxb2 33. Rxb7 Bc1
$18) 28... Kg7 29. g4 (29. Rxb7 $142 {seems even better} c4 30. Ne4 $18) 29...
