9. h4 $146 {Black has a cramped position} (9. Rd1 Bd7 10. O-O Nc6 11. h3 Rc8
12. Nb3 Be6 13. Qc1 a5 14. Bb5 Nd7 15. f4 Nb4 16. Nd4 Bc4 17. Bxc4 Rxc4 18. a3
