-Hess,R (2330) Germany 1992 1/2-1/2 (45)}) 9. cxb6 Qxb6 10. Qc2 h6 {Black
threatens to win material: h6xg5} 11. Bh4 O-O 12. Be2 Rb8 (12... Bb7 13. Ne5
Qd8 14. Qb3 Nxe5 15. Qxb7 $11) 13. Rb1 (13. O-O $5 $14) 13... c5 $11 14. dxc5
Bxc5 15. O-O Bd6 16. Rfc1 Bb7 17. Na4 {White threatens to win material: Na4xb6}
Qa7 18. Qd3 Rfc8 19. Bd1 (19. Nd4 Kh8 $11) 19... Ne4 20. Bc2 Rc7 21. Nd2 Nxd2
$4 {ruins a clearly superior position} (21... Ne5 $142 {the only rescuing move}
22. Qe2 Rbc8 23. Nxe4 dxe4 $15) 22. Qh7+ Kf8 23. Qh8# 1-0

