14... Nxe7 $11 15. Kxg2 c6 16. c5 {White wins space} Ng6 17. cxd6 Qxd6 {
White has a new backward pawn: d3} 18. Re1 Nd7 (18... Rbd8 19. Re3 $11) 19. d4
$14 Rfe8 20. dxe5 Qxd1 21. Rcxd1 Ndxe5 22. Nxe5 Nxe5 23. Bxe5 Rxe5 {A double
rook endgame occured} 24. Rd7 Kf8 25. f4 {White threatens to win material:
