Kf7 32. Red1 Rh8 {Black threatens to win material: Rh8xh4} 33. Kg3 Rhe8 (33...
Rh5 34. R1d3 $11) 34. Rd7 $14 Ke6 (34... Rxd7 35. Rxd7+ Re7 36. Rxe7+ Kxe7 37.
Kf3 $18) 35. Rxe7+ (35. R1d6+ Kf7 $16) 35... Rxe7 36. a4 (36. Rd8 Rc7 $14)
36... b6 (36... Re8 37. a5 $11) 37. Kg4 {[%cal Yf4f5] White plans f5} (37. Rd8
a5 38. bxa5 bxa5 $16) 37... Rh7 (37... f5+ 38. Kg5 fxe4 39. Kxg6 $14) 38. f5+
$14 gxf5+ 39. exf5+ Ke5 40. Re1+ Kd5 41. Re6 {White threatens to win material:
