Rxb6 $11) 42. h5 (42. a5 $142 bxa5 43. bxa5 $14) 42... c5 $4 {with this move
Black loses his initiative} (42... a5 $142 {would bring relief} 43. bxa5 bxa5
$11) 43. Rxb6 $18 c4 (43... cxb4 44. Rxb4 Ke5 45. Rb7 $18) 44. b5 (44. Rxa6
$142 {might be the shorter path} Rh7 45. b5 $18) 44... axb5 45. Rxb5+ $4 {
allows the opponent back into the game.} (45. axb5 $142 {and White is on the
